    {
      "bookmarkId": "24979310_5_860-897",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "860-897",
      "markText": "人们常说，每个人的世界都是一个圆，学习是半径，半径越大，拥有的世界也越大。",
      "totalCount": 896,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24979310&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=860&rangeEnd=897",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c3032ee0717d276ec306c2c?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=860&rangeEnd=897"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24979310_7_716-761",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "716-761",
      "markText": "精通书本理论的目的，“全在于应用”。所谓“应用”，就是通过阅读来满足个人或社会实践的需要。",
